{"tid":1670530,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［有圖］新一屆特區政府班子已定 唔係陳德霖唐英年","createTime":"2019-10-23T04:16:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T05:31:04.000Z","uid":287032,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c948bd3609fa210d56ce85b5ecd4c3e97e78fbb5","tid":1670530,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T04:16:40.000Z","msg":"其實睇繼任人<br />\n中共有一套邏輯<br />\n就係現任，繼任，有權力既<br />\n會以<span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">黑髮示人</span></strong></span><br />\n以退任既就會以白髮出席活動<br />\n以形成一個襯托<br />\n首先睇返閱兵<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3B2JN5S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3B2JN5S.jpg&h=ac515e0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n小熊克勤肛交都係以黑髮出席<br />\n代表佢地仍然有權力<br />\n而胡撚塗同溫家寶就一頭蒼白<br />\n代表佢地已經係任何實握權力<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實睇返上次特首對話會<br />\n幾乎肯定係為未來班子洗白<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/23KgoDe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F23KgoDe.png&h=dbaf8e52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n根據頭髮顏色定律<br />\n將會係：<br />\n<br />\n特首：陳肇始<br />\n財政司：邱騰華<br />\n政務司：聶德權<br />\n<br />\n佢地亦都係暫時民調中屬於較高既幾位<br />\n垃圾桶就係陪襯用既<br />\n<br />\n再睇返呢張相，係頒布緊急法既時候影<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gjkn3BD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGjkn3BD.jpg&h=c073fe04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n可以預計黃錦星楊痿雄黃偉綸可以留低<br />\n而佢地民調亦屬於高於平均數<br />\n楊潤雄雖然民望低<br />\n但係可能因為奶共奶得出色可以留低<br />\n<br />\n假波華比卡超雖然係黑髮<br />\n但一定唔會留任，因為佢地係眾矢之的<br />\n<br />\n至於幾時換<br />\n應該真係三月前換哂<br />\n因為之前有傳777辭職<br />\n佢係出聲明<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">強烈否認</span></span><br />\n今次就變成<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">不評論</span></span>"},{"pid":"25a0f6c136cf4bc7d6115459dc83bf86773c8963","tid":1670530,"uid":15224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T04:18:25.000Z","msg":"呢個世界有美源髮彩"},{"pid":"212261a227372e50ca3123b8849e239e1f97332c","tid":1670530,"uid":168619,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T04:18:34.000Z","msg":"欣賞你有諗法 <br />\n拉"},{"pid":"3b9bf3a74bff15c9aa8293fb4874896cc13882e6","tid":1670530,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T04:18:44.000Z","msg":"不過就算換完都係全部垃圾"},{"pid":"114b94074d0ca608ead56f4cc3dfb437d0b2563a","tid":1670530,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25a0f6c136cf4bc7d6115459dc83bf86773c8963","tid":1670530,"uid":15224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T04:18:25.000Z","msg":"呢個世界有美源髮彩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T04:19:35.000Z","msg":"支共對官員頭髮有嚴格標準<br />\n唔可以隨便染髮"},{"pid":"a8f08e9d060eb22a5c638dacc92696688c620fb1","tid":1670530,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T04:20:20.000Z","msg":"當年簿晞來受審都將佢變哂白髮黎審"},{"pid":"efbe0f5635f9ee4a9dcc907334b7c1a0d22d82f1","tid":1670530,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T04:24:48.000Z","msg":"比負皮講下原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"356443fe65bc3b6edf7bdbb70de14c1f7103fa62","tid":1670530,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T05:31:04.000Z","msg":"推"}]}